  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "16101d92619bb4f629e43b58f8e1696b23177ae051c7b2935996873e4ccf5a5e": "Hello, [?]. Did you speak to the Makeover Mage?",
    "193d64531605a574521c7366cbf8b853e7f7635572e0fcb45c8c7ea3000571aa": "Hello, [?].",
    "23a42a369e32e01896e14ace448d9f67f9a9b19a6ecce4647b728af12c062935": "Ah, [?]. The machine is nearly ready. When I activate it, it will bombard the fungus ring with magical energy.",
    "2adbaa37c906c609e202c8e81545976419eeb6d725455157ca86cfd31eac80e6": "Come on, Zanik. [?], will you meet us by the fungus ring to the south of the city?",
    "3534f0659bffff8080e35b4c45659b9c6288816510eab73832a3f1725a1c01aa": "[?]? What's going on? Where's Zanik?",
    "615fdafa76685ea23cb7b31fdfccfbb11cefc3bfa1b67c00577dfff46039e06f": "Hello, [?]. Have you found out anything about Yu'biusk yet?",
    "677a258eb141f51597a022c6d42773c02c34f835462baa13ea572e2451bd0cca": "Hello, [?]. What did you find in the Goblin Temple?",
    "6cfcc936727388901f728e6e92069e22558c4b4aa394c70cb2b0daa6432eda72": "Hello, [?]. Have you discovered anything in the Goblin Temple?",
    "79bf7fa096b3681392b01a21125db52fec83704733c27a539feee84d20551d1b": "Hello, [?]. Any luck getting into the Goblin Temple?",
    "8d4d51c4961ca8aded8157467fef07f707b0c63d0734d09c8bfe223f7c327730": "For this to work, we'll need to make sure the power is distributed correctly between the three circles of fungi. I need to handle the activation. [?], could you please handle the power distribution?",
    "a0726307bf467d14d4b28f73111aec4fdd24c748de4f60396be582cc4d684c51": "[?], Zanik, are you ready to leave?",
    "a94fc8a2f667b069f294a4aabcafe60738eec541de1a5e1373ee6e5b681192cc": "[?]. We should head back through the portal. Zanik is waiting on the other side.",
    "c918f064b216072678c22a7a5befbfc0049d9fba40d0ffec91dc649b972100af": "Excellent! I can make you [?] moving-over-distance spheres with them! How many do you want?",
    "dbe5572ae9b6d55563e1787451af7f1be61b92439d58bc54e217fc8f5179a423": "I know you will, [?]."
  }
